      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs like a dream and is perfect for anyone wanting a reliable, stylish car at a great value. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
