    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving naturally aspirated engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver 333 hp with a linear torque curve. Power is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery out of apexes. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, addressing common E46 platform weak points. The chassis remains taut, featuring MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry that provides precise feedback and high lateral grip. Finished in a driver-spec configuration, this M3 is an ideal candidate for the purist seeking a balanced, communicative performance machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
