    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-preserved example that strikes a perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and inviting; the leather seats are in great shape, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced regularly, with a recent professional inspection confirming the engine and transmission are in strong working order. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been smoke-free, garage-kept, and comes with a complete set of floor mats and a clear title. It\u2019s a reliable, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a premium driving experience.",
